name: Cognoma
tagline: Putting machine learning in the hands of cancer biologists.
body:
### Welcome to Cognoma!
The cognoma application will eventually live here. Right now, development is happening at [cognoma on github](http://github.com/cognoma). If you'd like to contribute, pitch in there. If you'd like this website to say more, file a pull request against this repository! :)
